### Background

@uncdr recently included the Horusec security scanning tool for open source projects in #9880, and it has found a few issues we should aim to resolve soon. See the failing CI build [here](https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/runs/4170016424?check_suite_focus=true) for a full list of problems discovered by Horusec. Most of these are minor fixes and dependency updates. We should resolve so that we can safely merge #9880 and have green PRs after that. This is a tracking issue to resolve the problems reported in #9880 and can be closed once those issues have been addressed. This is a good first issue for contributors.
